                        <h3>How secure is my financial data?</h3>
                        <span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Remindify uses bank-level 256-bit encryption to protect all your data. We never store your actual banking credentials, and all information is transmitted securely. Our security measures are regularly audited by independent security experts.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>Can I set up recurring bill reminders?</h3>
                        <span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes! You can set up reminders for bills that occur daily, weekly, monthly, quarterly, or annually. You can also set custom reminder schedules for bills with irregular payment dates.</p>
