                        <h3>How many bills can I track with Remindify?</h3>
                        <span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>The number of bills you can track depends on your subscription plan. The Basic plan allows up to 10 bills, while Premium and Business plans offer unlimited bill tracking.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-item" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>Can I access Remindify on my mobile device?</h3>
